{"tid":1380874,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 同我入哂黎！］夢遊目標一定要清晰表達","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:55.000Z","uid":272538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cecf4d30c0943ab778fb94a452fb2beb0be5959","tid":1380874,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚發夢聽到有手足話我哋再無<span style=\"color: blue;\">勇武</span>同<span style=\"color: blue;\">和理非</span>嘅分別，我哋只有<span style=\"color: red;\">前線</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">後援</span>。<br />\n<br />\n喺個刻我覺得大家已經忍受唔到等大台帶等人話你知做啲咩。我相信琴日逆行港島無街站大家都嗌足全程就感受到呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n係喇，大家都唔撚再驚彈唔撚再驚畀人打，但係大家會唔會覺得變左同狗仔對峙就淨係捱打同退防線？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z0LxdiErsLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ0LxdiErsLM&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67TDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=33b5d17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z0LxdiErsLM</a> （1:27:00)<br />\n立場姐姐係都提過一樣野，如果梁繼平無除低口罩係記者面前表達佔領立法會既原因既話，當晚既事件就真係被視為暴徒行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Only sheer violence is mute, and for this reason violence alone can never be great.</span></span> (Hannah Arendt)<br />\n<br />\n所以下次再有好似琴晚咁既發夢事件，我覺得有需要喺防線前對住記者講出我地訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 撒回惡法<br />\n2. 撒回6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 林鄭下台</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋喺畫面上做嘅行為，並唔足以令出面嘅人明白我哋發生緊啲乜嘢事。所以我哋一定要不斷地將我哋嘅行為，同我哋嘅言論掛鉤。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要講出口！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8a27a6448841e13de6b89c971fd5a6db0d80f75","tid":1380874,"uid":276191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"對極"},{"pid":"5c23ea4ed2577353c7b7b789fea3500d29f2b197","tid":1380874,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">岩!推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e3933080b14b6ae7224553c1ffc17bf267d83766","tid":1380874,"uid":281972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n賽後檢討，前中後排都入一入嚟睇吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380815/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380815/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"301ca67db6ade1fcead0676a93bcf51a442a91ce","tid":1380874,"uid":285536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"推 要講出口！"},{"pid":"4e754ae7d4944457ecba17e16e13b759f669f6ea","tid":1380874,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87d2e86e3b13293002f82e5e3f6a5272e8b0d69c","tid":1380874,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"推呀頂"},{"pid":"f380f0100f252fe3a32f7fbffb0917a57d0201a2","tid":1380874,"uid":241101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}